# Research Queue

Topics and entities queued for {{INSTANCE_NAME}}'s next research session. Add items here and {{INSTANCE_NAME}} will pick them up during off-peak research runs.

**Parent:** [[knowledge-base]]

## How to Use

Add items as unchecked checkboxes with context about what to look for:

```markdown
- [ ] Topic name — what to research and why it matters
```

{{INSTANCE_NAME}} will check items off as they're researched and integrated into the KB.

